      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nIt looks like MacOS find doesn't complain about repeated date specifications, just adding up the units as this patch currently does:\n\n $ find /tmp -mtime -7d\n /tmp\n\n $ find /tmp -mtime -35d\n /tmp\n /tmp/com.apple.launchd.xjUi2ZbNPr\n /tmp/com.apple.launchd.xjUi2ZbNPr/Render\n /tmp/.vbox-adilger-ipc\n /tmp/.vbox-adilger-ipc/ipcd\n /tmp/com.apple.launchd.WN9htxqT6g\n /tmp/com.apple.launchd.WN9htxqT6g/Listeners\n\n $ find /tmp -mtime -7d7d7d7d7d\n /tmp\n /tmp/com.apple.launchd.xjUi2ZbNPr\n /tmp/com.apple.launchd.xjUi2ZbNPr/Render\n /tmp/.vbox-adilger-ipc\n /tmp/.vbox-adilger-ipc/ipcd\n /tmp/com.apple.launchd.WN9htxqT6g\n /tmp/com.apple.launchd.WN9htxqT6g/Listeners",
